FLAVOUR_1_ADTEXT.message: THUIRLING AN LONG DE THUAIRT ar {planet}.

FLAVOUR_1_FAILUREMSG.message: Ní chreidim nár fhill tú roimhe seo! An méid ama seo curtha amú!

FLAVOUR_1_HOWMUCHTIMETEXT.message: Caithfidh tú filleadh roimh {due} chun aisíocaíocht iomlán ar chostaisí a fháil.

FLAVOUR_1_INTROTEXT.message: Tá lucht rialaithe aerthráchta {starport} ag lorg cúnaimh uait LÁITHREACH mar gheall ar spáslong de chineál {ship} a thuirling de thuairt ar {planet}. Níl a fhios againn an bhfuil an córas cothaithe beatha ag feidhmiú fós. Tá luach {cash} d'árachas ó spásphort {starport} ar an long chun costaisí práinnfhreagartha a chlúdach.

FLAVOUR_1_LOCATIONTEXT.message: Last known location for this ship was {planet} at latitude/longitude coordinates: {lat} / {long}. Ship ID is {shiplabel}.

FLAVOUR_1_SUCCESSMSG.message: Go raibh maith agat, is mór an faoiseamh é! Seolfaimid an t-airgead láithreach.

FLAVOUR_1_TYPEOFHELPTEXT.message: Tuairiscítear go bhfuil {crew} ball foirne agus {pass} paisinéir ar bord na loinge. Tá duine ag teastáil uainn chun an long a aimsiú, éinne a tháinig slán  a bhailiú, agus filleadh anseo leo ar an toirt.

FLAVOUR_2_ADTEXT.message: NÍL AON BHREOSLA FÁGTHA sa long ar a slí chun {starport}.

FLAVOUR_2_FAILUREMSG.message: Ní chreidim gur choinnigh tú ag fanacht mé chomh fada sin! Ní bhfaighidh tú cianóg rua uaim!

FLAVOUR_2_HOWMUCHTIMETEXT.message: Caithfidh tú an breosla a sheachadadh roimh {due} chun an íocaíocht iomlán a fháil.

FLAVOUR_2_INTROTEXT.message: Tá lucht rialaithe aerthráchta {starport} go díreach tar éis fógra a fháil go bhfuil {shiplabel} rite as breosla agus bhí sé orthu tuirlingt éigeandála a dhéanamh. D'íocfadh an píolóta {cash} as seirbhísí athbhreoslaithe.

FLAVOUR_2_LOCATIONTEXT.message: Tá an long ag fanacht ag domhanleithead {lat} / domhanfhad {long} ar phláinéad {planet}.

FLAVOUR_2_SUCCESSMSG.message: Go raibh míle maith agat! D'aistrigh mé an méid iomlán.

FLAVOUR_2_TYPEOFHELPTEXT.message: Tá an píolóta ag iarraidh {unit} tona de {cargo}.

FLAVOUR_3_ADTEXT.message: ÉIGEANDÁIL LEIGHIS ar long i ngar do {starport}.

FLAVOUR_3_FAILUREMSG.message: Unacceptable performance! We will update our records accordingly.

FLAVOUR_3_HOWMUCHTIMETEXT.message: The substitute pilot will need to reach the ship by {due}.

FLAVOUR_3_INTROTEXT.message: My name is {name} from {starport} air traffic control. I am requesting help in response to a medical emergency involving the pilot of flight {shiplabel} headed for {starport}.

FLAVOUR_3_LOCATIONTEXT.message: Rinne an long tuirlingt éigeandála ag comhordanáidí {lat} / {long}.

FLAVOUR_3_SUCCESSMSG.message: Thank you, commander! Your help has been duly noted.

FLAVOUR_3_TYPEOFHELPTEXT.message: Please transport a substitute pilot from {starport} to the ship so they can fly the ship back to {starport}.

FLAVOUR_4_ADTEXT.message: NÍL AON BHREOSLA FÁGTHA sa long ar {planet}.

FLAVOUR_4_FAILUREMSG.message: Seolfaidh mé duine éigin eile. Ná bac leis.

FLAVOUR_4_HOWMUCHTIMETEXT.message: For full pay the pilot expects you to deliver the fuel by {due}.

FLAVOUR_4_INTROTEXT.message: {starport} air traffic control has been contacted by the pilot of flight {shiplabel}. They are stranded with an empty fuel tank and have promised to pay {cash} to anyone that will refuel the ship.

FLAVOUR_4_LOCATIONTEXT.message: The ship is stranded on {planet} at coordinates {lat} / {long}.

FLAVOUR_4_SUCCESSMSG.message: Very good. We will recommend you for future assignments.

FLAVOUR_4_TYPEOFHELPTEXT.message: The pilot is asking for {unit} tons of {cargo}.

FLAVOUR_5_ADTEXT.message: NÍL AON BHREOSLA FÁGTHA sa long i ngar do {planet}.

FLAVOUR_5_FAILUREMSG.message: Ní féidir brath ar dhaoine a thuilleadh.

FLAVOUR_5_LOCATIONTEXT.message: The target ship is currently drifting within {dist} km from here. You will have to track down the exact location yourself.

FLAVOUR_5_SUCCESSMSG.message: We will make record of your timely completion of the task.

FLAVOUR_5_TYPEOFHELPTEXT.message: We request the delivery of {unit} tons of {cargo} to the ship.

FLAVOUR_6_ADTEXT.message: GAN FREAGRA ó long i réaltchóras {system}.

FLAVOUR_6_LOCATIONTEXT.message: Last known position was the vicinity of {planet} in the {system} [{sectorx},{sectory},{sectorz}] system, {dist} ly away from here.

FLAVOUR_6_SUCCESSMSG.message: Go raibh maith agat! Ní chreidfeá an faoiseamh a bhí orainn.

FLAVOUR_6_TYPEOFHELPTEXT.message: I need someone willing to leave immediately and bring our colleagues back to {starport}, should they be alive. The ship had {crew} crew and {pass} passengers on board.

FLAVOUR_7_ADTEXT.message: IMMEDIATE CREW TRANSPORT to the {system} system requested.

FLAVOUR_7_FAILUREMSG.message: Go raibh míle maith agat, ach tá tú ródhéanach!

FLAVOUR_7_HOWMUCHTIMETEXT.message: The replacement crew has to reach the ship by {due}.

FLAVOUR_7_INTROTEXT.message: My name is {name} of {entity}. Our only ship, {ship} {shiplabel}, is drifting with a crew of {crew} after {problem}. I am willing to pay {cash} for immediate help.

FLAVOUR_7_LOCATIONTEXT.message: You will find the ship in the {system} [{sectorx},{sectory},{sectorz}] system, {dist} ly from here. It is being kept in orbit around {planet}.

FLAVOUR_7_SUCCESSMSG.message: Thank you! I have been authorized to transmit the full payment.

FLAVOUR_7_TRANSFERMSG.message: Aistríodh {unit} go dtí an long sprice.

FLAVOUR_7_TYPEOFHELPTEXT.message: We can't return the ship without minimal crew present. I am searching for someone willing to transport a replacement crew of {deliver_crew} to our starship immediately.
